# Orchard Kubernetes Cluster

This directory will contain Kubernetes manifests and configuration for the Orchard cluster.

## Nodes
- apple (control plane + worker)
- lemon (worker)  
- plum (worker)

## Stack
- K3s (lightweight Kubernetes)
- Traefik Ingress Controller
- Future: Longhorn, MetalLB, ArgoCD

See `docs/architecture.md` for details.
